[{"category":"section","location":"#PkgBump","page":"Home","text":"Documentation for PkgBump.","title":"PkgBump"},{"category":"section","location":"#Description","page":"Home","text":"PkgBump.jl automatically increments the version in a Julia Project file. Package developers only have to run one of the three functions:\n\n# Roughly speaking\nbumppatch: v\"x.y.z\" -> v\"x.y.(z+1)\"\nbumpminor: v\"x.y.z\" -> v\"x.(y+1).0\"\nbumpmajor: v\"x.y.z\" -> v\"(x+1).0.0\"\n\nInternally, we use the Base.nextpatch, Base.nextminor, Base.nextmajor functions respectively.\n\n","title":"Description"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.bump-Tuple{Symbol}","page":"Home","text":"bump(mode::Symbol; commit=true, push=true)\n\nBumps the version of the current active project according to mode, commits the change to a new branch, and pushes the branch to the remote repository.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.bump"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.bumpmajor-Tuple{}","page":"Home","text":"bumpmajor(;kwargs)\n\nBump the major version of the current active project, commit, and push the changes.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.bumpmajor"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.bumpminor-Tuple{}","page":"Home","text":"bumpminor(;kwargs)\n\nBump the minor version of the current active project, commit, and push the changes.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.bumpminor"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.bumppatch-Tuple{}","page":"Home","text":"bumppatch(;kwargs)\n\nBump the patch version of the current active project, commit, and push the changes.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.bumppatch"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updatemajor!-Tuple{Pkg.Types.Project, AbstractString}","page":"Home","text":"updatemajor!(project::Pkg.Types.Project, project_file)\n\nIncrement the major version of the given project and write the changes to the project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updatemajor!"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updatemajor-Tuple{AbstractString}","page":"Home","text":"updatemajor(project_file::AbstractString)\n\nUpdate the major version of the project defined in project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updatemajor"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updateminor!-Tuple{Pkg.Types.Project, AbstractString}","page":"Home","text":"updateminor!(project::Pkg.Types.Project, project_file::AbstractString)\n\nIncrement the minor version of the given project and write the changes to the project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updateminor!"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updateminor-Tuple{AbstractString}","page":"Home","text":"updateminor(project_file::AbstractString)\n\nUpdate the minor version of the project defined in project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updateminor"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updatepatch!-Tuple{Pkg.Types.Project, AbstractString}","page":"Home","text":"updatepatch!(project::Pkg.Types.Project, project_file::AbstractString)\n\nIncrement the patch version of the given project and write the changes to the project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updatepatch!"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updatepatch-Tuple{AbstractString}","page":"Home","text":"updatepatch(project_file::AbstractString)\n\nUpdate the patch version of the project defined in project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updatepatch"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updateversion!-Tuple{Pkg.Types.Project, AbstractString, Symbol}","page":"Home","text":"updateversion!(project::Pkg.Types.Project, project_file::AbstractString, mode::Symbol)\n\nUpdate the version of the given project file according to the specified mode (:patch, :minor, :major). The new version is written directly to the project_file.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updateversion!"},{"category":"method","location":"#PkgBump.updateversion-Tuple{AbstractString, Symbol}","page":"Home","text":"updateversion(project_file::AbstractString, mode::Symbol) -> Pkg.Types.Project\n\nRead the project from project_file, update its version according to mode, and write the changes back. Returns the updated project.\n\n\n\n\n\n","title":"PkgBump.updateversion"}]
